s/2024/12/charli-xcx-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>已出演 Cathy Yan（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/birds-of-prey-review-harley-quinn-margot-robbie-2605306"><em>《猛禽小队</em></a>》）即将上映的电影<em>《The Gallerist</em> 》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Charli XCX – “Brat”评论：流行先锋完全拥抱舞池</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/12/the-gallerist-mrc-joins-cathy-yan-movie-natalie-portman-jenna-ortega-1236202386/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>报道，这位“小子”歌手已加入众星云集的演员阵容，其他演员包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jenna-ortega">珍娜·奥尔特加、</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/natalie-portman">娜塔莉·波特曼</a>、达文·乔伊·兰道夫、斯特林·K·布朗、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zach-galifianakis">扎克·加利费安纳</a>基斯、丹尼尔·布鲁尔和凯瑟琳·泽塔-琼斯。</p><p>这部电影讲述了一位绝望的画廊主密谋在迈阿密巴塞尔艺术展上出售尸体的故事，目前正在进行前期制作，预计将于今年年底拍摄。</p><p>上个月有消息称，XCX 已加入法国导演罗曼·加夫拉斯 (Romain Gavras) 的英文处女作<i>《牺牲》(Sacrifice)</i>的演员阵容。她将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anya-taylor-joy">安雅·泰勒-乔伊</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/furiosa-a-mad-max-saga"><i>《福瑞奥莎</i></a>》）、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-evans">克里斯·埃文斯</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame"><i>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</i></a> ）、文森特·卡塞尔（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-movie-11799-320528"><i>《黑天鹅》</i></a> ）和安比卡·莫德（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/one-day-review-netflix-leo-woodall-david-nicholls-3583811"><i>《一日</i></a>》）一起主演。</p><p>据报道，该片上个月正在希腊和保加利亚拍摄，该艺术家在影片中所扮演的角色细节尚未得到证实。在宣布的其他配角成员中，瑞典说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-lean">Yung Lean</a>是他的电影处女作，他还与 XCX 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a>合作混音了她的歌曲“360”。</p><p> XCX 目前有 7 个银幕项目正在进行中，包括格雷格·荒木 (Gregg Araki) 的<i>《我想要你的性</i>》和由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-corrin-reveals-the-deadpool-wolverine-death-that-made-them-feel-so-bad-3780930">艾玛·科林</a>( <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/deadpool-wolverine-review-marvel-3777877"><i>《死侍》和《金刚狼》</i></a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/maika-monroe-details-first-time-seeing-nicolas-cage-in-longlegs-makeup-3775626">麦卡·梦露</a>( <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/longlegs-review-nicolas-cage-maika-monroe-horror-3774136"><i>《长腿</i></a>》) 领衔的图画小说改编版<i>《英雄百夜</i>》。 </p><figure id="attachment_3822214" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822214" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822214" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin.jpg" alt="艾玛·科林和查理·XCX" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/emma-corrin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3822214" class="wp-caption-text">艾玛·科林 (Emma Corrin) 和查莉·XCX (Charli XCX) 出席《诺斯费拉图》洛杉矶首映式的余兴派对。图片来源：Kevin Winter/GA/The Hollywood Reporter via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>此前，她在11月担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>的表演和主持双重职责，不仅表演了她最新专辑中的曲目，而且在给人留下了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔</a>印象后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-to-charli-xcxs-adele-impersonation-on-snl-she-killed-this-3813446">，她的银幕能力和喜剧时机赢得了粉丝</a>的称赞。在一个短剧中。</p><p>她主导文化的第六张唱片“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> ”于六月发行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">并被<i>NME</i>评为年度专辑</a>。 “毫无疑问， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">‘小子’作为一种文化轰动</a>是值得一看的。但《Brat》作为一张专辑——发行时的核心唱片、营销背后的音乐——绝对是独一无二的，” <i>NME</i>指出。</p><p> “作为一名词曲作者和作词家，查理职业生涯的大部分时间都在顽固的态度和赤裸裸的脆弱之间摇摆不定。 《小子》在音阶上毫不费力地移动，给我们带来了坚如磐石的轰动，但仍然具有令人痛苦的人性。这张专辑不仅是 Charli 的巅峰之作，而且为现代流行音乐树立了新的标杆。” </p><figure id="attachment_3802004" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3802004" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802004" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe.jpg" alt="Charli XCX 在 Storm King 艺术中心摆姿势。亨利·雷德克利夫信用" width="2000" height="1600" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-400x320.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-800x640.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-696x557.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-1392x1114.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-1068x854.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3802004" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX 在 Storm King 艺术中心摆姿势。亨利·雷德克利夫信用</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">“Brat”夏季</a>演出预计将于 2025 年进行第二轮演出。Charli <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announced-as-first-parklife-2025-headliner-buy-tickets-3815857">已被确认为明年 Parklife 的首位主角</a>，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-charli-xcxs-star-studded-360-video-with-julia-fox-chloe-sevigny-and-many-more-3755245">“360”</a>艺术家还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-to-headline-and-curate-own-party-girl-festival-at-londons-lido-2025-buy-tickets-3815487">在伦敦 LIDO 音乐节上策划一天的演出，届时她将带来一场超值表演</a>。</p><p>此外，她还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-huge-summer-2025-shows-in-belfast-and-dublin-3814479">在贝尔法斯特和都柏林举办两场户外演出</a>，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">2025 年 Coachella</a>音乐节上表演，并在巴塞罗那和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">波尔图</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-says-she-chappell-roan-and-sabrina-carpenter-headlining-primavera-sound-2025-is-the-holy-trinity-3806307">Primavera Sound 上表演</a>。除此之外，她还宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-us-brat-arena-tour-2025-buy-tickets-3815161">将于四月和五月进行美国舞台巡演</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/charli-xcx-joins-new-film-alongside-jenna-ortega-and-natalie-portman-3822201">Charli XCX 与 Jenna Ortega 和 Natalie Portman 一起加入新电影，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
